The paper deals with face recognition using thermal images, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) domain. The proposed method involves the use of a generative adversarial network (GAN), which is a popular deep learning technique used in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves image processing and manipulation, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) domains.
